   a timely and effective fashion in this big data era has become
   difficult. In this study, we delve into this issue by trying to identify
   the core disseminators in the dissemination process. We propose the
   concept of a disinformation channel and quantitatively analyse these
   company-related disinformation channels among media outlets. By
   empirically analysing 4,689 disinformation news values and 330 channels
   in 2018, we reveal that the disinformation values and negative news
   values are characteristics. We also build automatic identification
