Abstract = {{Previous research has described how highly personalised paid advertising
   on social media platforms can be used to influence voter preferences and
   undermine the integrity of elections. However, less work has examined
   how search engine optimisation (SEO) strategies are used to target
   audiences with disinformation or political propaganda. This paper looks
   at 29 junk news domains and their SEO keyword strategies between January
   2016 and March 2019. I find that SEO - rather than paid advertising - is
   the most important strategy for generating discoverability via Google
   Search. Following public concern over the spread of disinformation
   online, Google's algorithmic changes had a significant impact on junk
