   distortions of reality, during the health crisis caused by COVID-19 they
   have become an added problem by proposing and affirming to audiences
   forms of prevention, procedures or medicines that not only do not serve
   to prevent this disease, but can even be counterproductive or harmful.
   It is here that the detection of false news plays an essential role, as
