Abstract = {{The current media ecosystem has generated new forms of manipulation and
   disinformation, used in political issues of greater complexity, such as
   the independence referendum held in Catalonia on October 1, 2017. The
   objective of this research is to analyze the characteristics of the fake
   news and the most widespread hoaxes about this topic and make a
   cartography of the generative strategies of the 80 hashtags that became
   trending topics on Twitter during the crisis. By using documentary
