   disinformation campaigns. Fake news poses a serious threat to the
   functioning and safety of our society, as demonstrated by
   nation-state-sponsored campaigns to sway the 2016 US presidential
   election, and more recently COVID-19 pandemic hoaxes that promote false
   cures, putting lives at risk.
   FADE is a novel approach and service that helps Internet users detect
   fake news. FADE discovers multiple news sources covering the same story,
   analyzes their reputation, and checks the trustworthiness of cited
