   believe that this situation will not improve in the coming years. By
   2022, half of the news will be fake news. In terms of users, young
   people and adults have problems understanding where the information they
   find online comes from and what sources to trust or not. In order to
   ascertain the degree of credibility that young users in Andalucia give
