   social media platforms to agree a voluntary Code of Practice on
   Disinformation. Signatories to this, including Facebook, Google and
   Twitter, committed to `ensuring transparent, fair and trustworthy online
   campaign activities ahead of the European elections in spring 2019'
   (Kirk, N., Culloty, E., Casey, E., Teeling, L., Park, K., Kearns, C.
