Abstract = {{Online political advertisements have become an important element in
   electoral campaigning throughout the world. At the same time, concepts
   such as disinformation and manipulation have emerged as a global
   concern. Although these concepts are distinct from online political ads
   and data-driven electoral campaigning, they tend to share a similar
   trait related to valence, the intrinsic attractiveness or averseness of
