   digital technologies bring in humanitarian settings and ensure relevant
   protection responses in the digital age. Marelli is Head of the ICRC's
   Data Protection Office (DPO). During his tenure with the ICRC, the
   organization has chartered new pathways for how it can carry out its
   operational work, while ensuring that the data of the affected people
   which it serves, as well those of its employees, are well protected.
