   model where users of the digital media can appropriate the contents,
   recreate, and circulate them. In this context, online social media are a
   suitable circuit for the distribution of fake news and the spread of
   disinformation. Particularly, photo and video editing tools and recent
   advances in artificial intelligence allow non-professionals to easily
   counterfeit multimedia documents and create deep fakes. To avoid the
   spread of disinformation, some online social media deploy methods to
